2	//
3	// Writes go through this route instead of the browser Supabase client so that:
4	//   * The insert uses the service-role connection (DIRECT_URL) which bypasses
5	//     the browser-client auth / RLS layer entirely.
6	//   * requireEmployee() validates the session server-side — the same path that
7	//     already works for every other server component.
